{"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"EudiWalletKit"}],"title":"Get started","roleHeading":"Article"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/ManageDocuments","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/SecureAreas","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/PresentationService","doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/WalletUI"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Essentials","title":"Essentials"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Package installation","anchor":"Package-installation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To use EUDI Wallet Kit, add the following dependency to your Package.swift:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["dependencies: [","\t\t.package(url: \"https:\/\/github.com\/eu-digital-identity-wallet\/eudi-lib-ios-wallet-kit.git\", .upToNextMajor(from: \"0.6.6\"))","]"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then add the Eudi Wallet package to your target’s dependencies:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["dependencies: [","\t\t.product(name: \"EudiWalletKit\", package: \"eudi-lib-ios-wallet-kit\"),","]"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Initialization","anchor":"Initialization","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWallet","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class provides a unified API for the two user attestation presentation flows. It is initialized with a document storage manager instance. For SwiftUI apps, the wallet instance can be added as an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentObject"},{"type":"text","text":" to be accessible from all views. A KeyChain implementation of document storage is available."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\tlet certificates = [\"pidissuerca02_cz\", \"pidissuerca02_ee\", \"pidissuerca02_eu\", \"pidissuerca02_lu\", \"pidissuerca02_nl\", \"pidissuerca02_pt\", \"pidissuerca02_ut\"]","    wallet = try! EudiWallet(serviceName: \"my_wallet_app\", trustedReaderCertificates: certificates.map { Data(name: $0, ext: \"der\")! }, logFileName: \"temp.txt\")","    wallet.userAuthenticationRequired = true","    wallet.openID4VpConfig = OpenId4VpConfiguration(clientIdSchemes: [.x509SanDns, .x509Hash])","    wallet.transactionLogger = MyFileTransactionLogger(wallet: wallet)","\twallet.loadAllDocuments()"]},{"type":"heading","text":"BLE Transfer Mode","anchor":"BLE-Transfer-Mode","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWallet\/bleTransferMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property controls the Bluetooth Low Energy role used during proximity (ISO 18013-5) presentation."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can set it during initialization via "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWalletConfiguration\/bleTransferMode","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" or update it later on the wallet instance:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"code":".server","type":"codeVoice"}]},{"type":"text","text":" (default): The holder device acts as a GATT peripheral (server), advertising and waiting for the reader to connect."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"code":".client","type":"codeVoice"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The holder device acts as a GATT central (client), scanning and connecting to the reader’s peripheral."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".both","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": The holder device supports both modes simultaneously and advertises both in the QR device engagement."}]}]}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let config = EudiWalletConfiguration(","    serviceName: \"my_wallet_app\",","    trustedReaderCertificates: [Data(name: \"eudi_pid_issuer_ut\", ext: \"der\")!],","    bleTransferMode: .server  \/\/ default; use .client or .both as needed",")","let wallet = try! EudiWallet(eudiWalletConfig: config)","wallet.bleTransferMode = .client"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"OpenID4VCI Configuration","anchor":"OpenID4VCI-Configuration"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The wallet now supports multiple OpenID4VCI issuer configurations for enhanced flexibility. You can configure the wallet with a dictionary of issuer configurations:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Configure multiple OpenID4VCI issuers with DPoP support","let issuerConfigurations: [String: OpenId4VciConfiguration] = [","    \"eudi_pid_issuer\": OpenId4VciConfiguration(","        credentialIssuerURL: \"https:\/\/pid.issuer.example.com\",","        requireDpop: true,","        issuerMetadataPolicy: .requireSigned,","        dpopKeyOptions: KeyOptions(","            secureAreaName: \"SecureEnclave\", curve: .P256, accessControl: .requireUserPresence","        )","    ),","    \"mdl_issuer\": OpenId4VciConfiguration(","        credentialIssuerURL: \"https:\/\/mdl.issuer.example.com\",","        requireDpop: false,","        issuerMetadataPolicy: .ignoreSigned","    )","]","","\/\/ Register additional issuers after initialization","try wallet.registerOpenId4VciServices(issuerConfigurations)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"code":"issuerMetadataPolicy","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to control signed metadata handling per issuer:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".requireSigned"},{"text":" for issuers that require signed metadata validation","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".ignoreSigned"},{"type":"text","text":" for environments that still use unsigned metadata"}]}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/getstarted"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to install and initialize EUDI Wallet Kit in your project"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/GetStarted"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"article","references":{"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/WalletUI":{"url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/walletui","role":"sampleCode","abstract":[],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/WalletUI","kind":"article","title":"EUDI iOS Wallet reference implementation"},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/EudiWallet":{"abstract":[{"text":"User wallet implementation","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"EudiWallet","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/EudiWallet","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"EudiWallet","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/eudiwallet","title":"EudiWallet"},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/ManageDocuments":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/EudiWalletKit\/documentation\/EudiWalletKit\/ManageDocuments","url":"\/documentation\/eudiwalletkit\/managedocuments","title":"Manage documents","kind":"article","role":"article","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The EudiWallet class provides a set of methods to work with documents.","type":"text"}]},"doc://EudiWalletKit/documentation/EudiWalletKit/EudiWa